WEBVTT

00:00:30.080 --> 00:00:32.816
Ali usprkos njegovom uspjehu,

00:00:32.840 --> 00:00:35.160
profesionalnom i osobnom,

00:00:36.080 --> 00:00:38.360
Clydeova priča ima tužan završetak.

00:00:39.440 --> 00:00:40.640
U 2010.,

00:00:41.720 --> 00:00:43.480
u 62. godini života,

00:00:44.640 --> 00:00:47.640
Clyde je umro od krvnog ugruška u plućima.

00:00:50.120 --> 00:00:53.920
Clyde nije jedini koji je to doživio.

00:00:54.720 --> 00:00:57.576
Mnogo njegovih crnih kolega s Yale-a

00:00:57.600 --> 00:00:59.080
je također umrlo mlado.